ach diamond seal is worth 15-20 gold, saphires 5-7g and emeralds about 2g.  Yes, one quick run can yield awesome money. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/utonewango.showPublicProfile?language=EN>tonewango</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#330000>(8/16/02 10:09:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fguildmessageboards68349frm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spellcrafting / Alchemy</span><hr size=1> In case anyone was in doubt, I will not be participating in crafting even with the new Spellcrafting/Alchemy skills coming up.  However, I am very interested in receiving the benefits of these skills and am standing ready to donate some plat to the cause.  Please don't be shy in asking me for money so that you can raise these skills...I will definitely not be shy in asking you for some services once you have achieved the proficiency ;-)<br><br>Wango<br>Toneloch <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/uguev23.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Guev23</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#330000>(8/16/02 11:21:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fguildmessageboards68349frm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spellcrafting / Alchemy</span><hr size=1> Wow Excellent post Tread. Below is what I found are the important parts of Tread's link.<br><br>2 hours in DF yesterday got me 40 diamond seals (princess drops fiery sets, group killed her twice, plus all the regular seal drops from her room and the ramp area. 40 diamond seals = 2 Avernal Coifs = 286 diamond bars in salvage = 143 diamond hinges = 639 gold. If you aren't a crafter, then find one with half a brain and sell him the seals. I buy them for 8-10g or so each (that might sound low since you know how much I'm going to make from them, but you have to consider what a PITA it is to hinge all those bars out).&quot;<br><br>Emerald Seals: Avernal Maligned Spiked Mace = 28 seals = 13 diamond bars <br>Sapphire Seals: Daemon Forged Hauberk = 32 seals = 46 diamond bars <br>Diamond Seals: Avernal Coif = 20 seals = 143 diamond bars<br><br>That sounds like a huge amount of cash just farming the princess for a few hours could mean 3-4k in gold for us.  Anytime anyone wants to go count me in.<br><br>Guev<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/uguev23.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Guev23</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#330000>(8/16/02 11:25:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fguildmessageboards68349frm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spellcrafting / Alchemy</span><hr size=1> Just to clarify the real cash we will need will not be to increase crafting but to pay for our new armor.  I think we will each need about 3k or so,  Leather and rf wearers will need much less than scale wearers.<br><br>I do have 99 qual af 102 boots and gloves for all guild rf wearers in chomskys inventory which is somewhat of a start.<br><br>But I think we need a few good days in df.  If anyone wants to to set a raid tommorow or Sunday set up a time on the raid schedule and count me in.<br><br>Guev <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://